    "title": "Njaa",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "njaa",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Njaa ilitokea mapema katika maisha ya mababu Abrahamu na Isaka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10\">Mwanzo 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1\">26:1</a>). Wakati familia ya babu Yakobo ilipokumbwa na njaa, Mungu tayari alikuwa amempeleka mwanawe Yosefu katika Misri ili kusaidia watu wa Mungu kupitia mgogoro huo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:56-Gen42:5\">41:56–42:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:5\">45:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:7\">7</a>). Ukame huu ulikuwa mkali sana. Hata hivyo, ukame ulikuwa jambo la kawaida katika ulimwengu wa kale (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:1\">Ruthu 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1\">2 Samweli 21:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:1-1Kgs18:2\">1 Wafalme 18:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:1-Hag1:11\">Hagai 1:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28\">Matendo 11:28</a>).</p><p>Njaa ilikuwa janga kubwa katika jamii za kilimo. Ukame, kushindwa kwa mazao, au kuzingirwa kunaweza kusababisha njaa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:1-2Kgs25:30\">2 Wafalme 25:1–30</a>). Njaa mara nyingi ilikuja pamoja na magonjwa au vita, na kuathiri viwango mbalimbali vya jamii (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:12\">Yeremia 14:12</a>). Hii pia iliathiri wanyama (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:20\">Yoeli 1:20</a>). Watu walitegemea mvua, na hivyo baadhi yao walihifadhi chakula ili kujiandaa kwa ajili ya njaa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:33-Gen41:36\">Mwanzo 41:33–36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:23-Gen47:24\">47:23–24</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr26:15\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 26:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:11\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 31:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:37-Neh10:39\">Nehemia 10:37–39</a>).</p><p>Wakati chakula kilipokuwa hakitoshi, mambo mengi mabaya yalitokea (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10\">Mwanzo 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1\">26:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:24-2Kgs6:29\">2 Wafalme 6:24–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:1-Neh5:3\">Nehemia 5:1–3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer19:9\">Yeremia 19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:20-Lam2:21\">Maombolezo 2:20–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:8-Lam4:10\">4:8–10</a>).</p><ul><li><p>Chakula kilikuwa cha gharama kubwa sana.</p></li><li><p>Watu waliiba kutoka kwa wenzao.</p></li><li><p>Maskini walitendewa bila haki.</p></li><li><p>Mashamba hayakuweza kuzalisha mazao.</p></li><li><p>Watu walilazimika kuondoka kwenye nyumba zao ili kutafuta chakula.</p></li><li><p>Kwenye hali mbaya zaidi, watu walilazimika kula hata nyama ya binadamu ili kuendelea kuishi.</p></li></ul><p>Wakati mwingine, watu waliona njaa kama adhabu kutoka kwa Mungu dhidi ya Waisraeli (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:14-Lev26:20\">Mambo ya Walawi 26:14–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:16-Deut11:17\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 11:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:33\">28:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:17-Jer29:18\">Yeremia 29:17–18</a>). Kwa hiyo, kuwa mwaminifu kwa Mungu ilikuwa muhimu sana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:18-Ps33:19\">Zaburi 33:18–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:19\">37:19</a>). Baraka za Mungu kwa taifa zilijumuisha ulinzi dhidi ya njaa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:29\">Ezekieli 34:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:29-Ezek36:30\">36:29–30</a>).</p><p>Yesu alikumbana na njaa kama ile ya Israeli wakati wa kipindi chake nyikani. Alichagua kutotengeneza mkate kwa ajili yake mwenyewe (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1-Matt4:4\">Mathayo 4:1–4</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 8:3</a>). Mafanikio yake dhidi ya majaribu ya shetani yalionyesha kwamba ukosefu wa chakula na njaa vinaweza kujenga unyenyekevu na imani katika utunzaji wa Mungu. Yesu aliwalisha watu elfu tano ili kuwaonyesha kwamba yeye ni &quot;mkate wa uzima,&quot; &quot;mkate wa kweli kutoka kwa Mungu ambao  unatoka mbinguni (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:32-John6:35\">Yohana 6:32–35</a>).</p><p>Hata hivyo, umati ulimfuata zaidi kwa ajili ya chakula kuliko kwa ajili ya yeye ni nani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:26-John6:27\">Yohana 6:26–27</a>). Ingawa hakupuuza chakula cha kimwili, Yesu alisisitiza umuhimu wa njaa na kiu ya kiroho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:21\">Luka 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">Yohana 4:34</a>). Kula hutumika kama mazingira na ishara ya ushirika (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:34\">Mwanzo 43:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:15-Luke22:16\">Luka 22:15–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:9\">Ufunuo 19:9</a>). Mbinguni, njaa haitakuwepo tena (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">Ufunuo 7:16</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10\">Mwanzo 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1\">26:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:33-Gen41:36\">41:33–36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:56-Gen41:57\">56–57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:6-Gen45:7\">45:6–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:19-Lev26:20\">Mambo ya Walawi 26:19–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:3\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:16-Deut11:17\">11:16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:1\">Ruthu 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1\">2 Samweli 21:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:1-1Kgs18:2\">1 Wafalme 18:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:1-2Kgs8:2\">2 Wafalme 8:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:11-Jer14:16\">Yeremia 14:11–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:29-Ezek34:31\">Ezekieli 34:29–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:28-Ezek36:32\">36:28–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:1-Joel1:20\">Yoeli 1:1–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:11-Amos8:14\">Amosi 8:11–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:1-Hag1:11\">Hagai 1:1–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:21\">Luka 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:32-John6:35\">Yohana 6:32–35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28-Acts11:30\">Matendo 11:28–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:16\">Ufunuo 7:16</a></p>",
